        Service providing recommendations for a query.
        Parameters:
        origin - Origin of the query.
        req - HTTP request.
        servletResp - HTTP response.
        queryStr - Query of format QF1 or QF2 (both are supported).
        Returns:
        A set of recommendations. The format is RF1 (respectively RF2) if the format of the query is QF1 (respectively QF2).

      • getCoOccurrenceGraph

        public javax.ws.rs.core.Response getCoOccurrenceGraph(@HeaderParam(value="origin")
                                             java.lang.String origin,
                                             @Context
                                             javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest req,
                                             @Context
                                             javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse servletResp)
        Service providing access to the co-occurrence graph. The co-occurrence graph is supposed to be up-to-date at any time (no caching).
        Parameters:
        origin - Origin of the query.
        req - HTTP request.
        servletResp - HTTP response.
        Returns:
        A co-occurrence graph.
        See Also:
        CacheReader

      • getMaximalCliques

        public javax.ws.rs.core.Response getMaximalCliques(@HeaderParam(value="origin")
                                          java.lang.String origin,
                                          @Context
                                          javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest req,
                                          @Context
                                          javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse servletResp)
        Services providing the set of cliques contained in the co-occurrence graph. Each clique is a graph. As the computation of cliques is very time-consuming, a cached version is returned. The frequency at which the cache is updated is not fixed (yet): every day, every hour, etc.
        Parameters:
        origin - Origin of the query.
        req - HTTP request.
        servletResp - HTTP response.
        Returns:
        A set of cliques.
        See Also:
        Clique
